default 
defaultsector and the Government that highlights some 
defaultof those ways of measuring and ensuring that you get the ongoing dialogue and monitoring through the life of the contract.
defaultRicharddefault defaultMacfarlanedefault: The simple answer is that you simply follow good procurement practice.
default 
defaultAt the beginning, Matthew referred to starting the contract with, “These are our objectives”.
default 
defaultIf you put the social
default-
defaultvalue bit at the beginning of the tender, it is not actually clear what you want the contractor to do.
default 
