default 
defaultThis is what you have to deliver: this, this, this and this.”
default 
defaultYou then have some 
defaultmeasurables
default.
defaultQ358 default&#xa0; 
defaultMark defaultPawseydefault:default Is it your view that potential suppliers understand those objectives?
default 
defaultDo they buy in to those objectives?
defaultRicharddefault defaultMacfarlanedefault: Initially, what you are doing is changing the market.
default 
defaultYou are tweaking the market not just to provide a service, but now provide a service and provide some social value, and this is the social value.
default 
