defaultQ359 default&#xa0; 
defaultMark defaultPawseydefault:default How capable do you think small businesses are of achieving those objectives?
defaultRicharddefault defaultMacfarlanedefault: They are more capable than they think they are.
default 
defaultComing back to construction, where most of this has happened, most traineeships and apprenticeships happen in small firms.
default 
defaultFrom the construction
default-
defaultskills point of view, that is where most of the opportunities are.
default 
