defaultDr defaultTellesdefault:default For my background, I would say that, more than creating opportunities specifically for SMEs or micro-companies, the important bit is to find new procedures and new ways to award contracts, which solve the problems you have highlighted very well and are more attuned to the needs of low
default-
defaultvalue contracts.
