defaultQ364 default&#xa0; 
defaultChair:default You have gone on to argue that some authorities are really doing no more than engaging protectionist policies under the guise of helping local economies and that, if all authorities do this, there is no overall benefit but probably an extra cost, in that you are not getting the best
default-
defaultvalue contractors bidding for work.
defaultDr defaultTellesdefault:default I was surprised when I came to the 
defaultUK
default.
default 
defaultI used to be a lawyer in 
defaultPortugal
default and 
defaultSpain
default and I worked a lot in public procurement.
default 
