default-
defaultvalue tenders, which is very expensive for an SME in terms of time and effort to bid for these.
default 
defaultSuppliers also fear the repercussions of making the wrong decisions.
default 
defaultThey try to use belt and braces, and make the process far too complex, which is not good for them, because it takes a long time to take part in this.
