default 
defaultIn terms of the aggregation, ESPO aggregated the requirements and streamlined the SLAs, which is a great idea, but, in terms of going back out to tender, they should have still made it available to the SMEs and larger companies, because there are a lot of benefits to be had from that.
defaultAll in all, the skills are there, but we need a bit more guidance on what is appropriate for the size of the tender so that people feel confident about running a tender that way, without the risk of something going wrong.
defaultQ369 default&#xa0; 
